Source code for the website http://highl.it

database schema:

CREATE TABLE images(
    id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
    height INTEGER,
    width  INTEGER,
    top    INTEGER,
    left   INTEGER,
    ext    TEXT,
    auth   TEXT
);

sample convert commands:
convert 1.jpg -crop 32x32+100+100 +repage 1crop.jpg

creates 32x32 image starting at 100,100

convert Y.jpg -matte -fill '#000a' -draw 'rectangle 0,0,300,300' blah.jpg

convert Y.jpg -matte -fill '#000a' -draw 'rectangle 0,0,10000,10000' blah.jpg 

convert blah.jpg -draw "image SrcOver 100,100 0,0 '../cimg/Y.jpg'" blah2.jpg

